<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/683457-this-unusual-book-was-first-published-in">This unusual book was first published in 1973 under the title &quot;Maus: A Survivor&#39;s Tale.&quot;

In 1991, this was followed &quot;Maus II: And Here my Troubles Began.&quot;

This is one of a kind essential reading. Do you agree ?

Peter Kubicek</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_683457'><a id="like_count_community_question_683457" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/683457?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">15 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F15195.The_Complete_Maus">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/683457-this-unusual-book-was-first-published-in">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
