        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1138236398" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6603124923986829623"><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1430398154i/14709433._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><a href='http://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/apr/28/art-spiegelman-russia-maus-bookstores-holocaust' rel='nofollow noopener'>Art Spiegelman warns of &apos;dangerous&apos; outcome as Russian shops ban Maus </a><br/><br/>This has been on my wishlist forever -looks like this is a good time to read it.<blockquote>
<b>&quot;My father pulled out 14 of his teeth to escape. If you missed 12 teeth they let you go.&quot;</b><br/>- page 45, book I<br/><br/><b>&quot;The guards, it was Jews with big sticks, they acted so, just like the Germans&quot;</b><br/>- page 106, book I</blockquote> <br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1430433898i/14713258._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1430476782i/14716440.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
  <span id="freeText6603124923986829623" style="display:none"><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1430398154i/14709433._SX540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><a href="http://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/apr/28/art-spiegelman-russia-maus-bookstores-holocaust" rel="nofollow noopener">Art Spiegelman warns of 'dangerous' outcome as Russian shops ban Maus </a><br><br>This has been on my wishlist forever -looks like this is a good time to read it.<blockquote>
